epg.title: Life in Pictures: Mark Webber
epg.desc:
| +TP | Deportes |

Nine-time grand prix winner Mark Webber spent 12 years in Formula 1, most of them in the teeth of adversity: from wrestling with sub-optimal machinery at Minardi and Jaguar to providing adult supervision at a young Red Bull Racing, and a not always happy partnership with Sebastian Vettel. We take you through Webber’s early career and path to F1, from his arrival in the UK and Formula Ford in 1996, to joining up with Benetton and Flavio Briatore in 2001 and his transition to Jaguar and eventually Red Bull Racing. All photos used are taken from Motorsport Images, the largest collection of motorsport pictures in the world. (Warning, video contains some explicit language)

epg.title: W2RC 2025: Rally Raid Portugal Prologue
epg.desc:
| +TP | Deportes |

The BP Ultimate Rally Raid Portugal kicked off in Grândola with a 5 km prologue, marking the start of its second edition. Daniel Sanders (Red Bull KTM) claimed his 20th special win in RallyGP, while Edgar Canet (Rally2), Thomas Zoldos (Rally3), and Antanas Kanopkinas (quads) also took victories. FIA leader Nasser Al Attiyah (Dacia) repeated his 2024 prologue win ahead of Toyota’s Lucas Moraes and João Ferreira, while Carlos Sainz (Ford) finished last in class. Portuguese fans celebrated local triumphs from Gonçalo Guerreiro (Challenger) and Alexandre Pinto (SSV). Stage 1, a 425 km loop around Grândola, begins on Wednesday at 8:05 am (UTC+1).

epg.title: W2RC 2025: Rally Raid Portugal Stage 1
epg.desc:
| +TP | Deportes |

Stage 1 of the bp Ultimate Rally Raid Portugal saw fierce battles on a 425 km loop around Grândola. Red Bull KTM’s Daniel Sanders (RallyGP) and Edgar Canet (Rally2) doubled up on their prologue wins, while Thomas Zoldos repeated in Rally3 and Gaëtan Martinez took the quad lead. In cars, Henk Lategan (Toyota) claimed the stage and overall lead ahead of four fellow Toyotas, as Nasser Al Attiyah (Dacia) slipped to eighth after a penalty. Mattias Ekström (Challenger) and Alexandre Pinto (SSV) also triumphed. Stage 2 heads into Spain with the week’s longest test: 655 km, including 429 against the clock.

epg.title: W2RC 2025: Rally Raid Portugal Stage 2
epg.desc:
| +TP | Deportes |

The bp Ultimate Rally Raid Portugal’s longest stage, a 655 km route from Grândola to Badajoz, delivered high drama on Thursday. Red Bull KTM’s Daniel Sanders edged Tosha Schareina in RallyGP, while teammate Edgar Canet extended his Rally2 lead. France’s Thomas Zoldos (Rally3) and Gaëtan Martinez (quads) dominated their classes, and João Ferreira (Toyota) claimed a breakthrough Ultimate win over mentor Carlos Sainz. Dacia endured setbacks as Nasser Al-Attiyah and Sébastien Loeb lost significant time. Portugal celebrated a historic triple in FIA categories with Ferreira, Gonçalo Guerreiro (Challenger), and Alexandre Pinto (SSV). Stage 3 will cover 511 km around Badajoz on Friday.

epg.title: W2RC 2025: Rally Raid Portugal Stage 3
epg.desc:
| +TP | Deportes |

Yesterday in Badajoz, Daniel Sanders deprived Tosha Schareina of a coveted home win by just 4 seconds, but the Spaniard got his own back today, edging out the Australian at the end of a lengthy duel. "Chucky" fought gallantly despite having to open the course but had to yield near the finish. Schareina secured his first win since stage 5 of the Abu Dhabi Desert Challenge by 3′18″ and rocketed into the overall lead. The two favourites are now 1′42″ apart in the race for the trophy. "Chucky", who had remained undefeated since the start of the bp Ultimate Rally Raid Portugal, was reminded that all good things must come to an end. Tomorrow, he will set out to take back control from the new...

epg.title: W2RC 2025: Rally Raid Portugal Stage 4
epg.desc:
| +TP | Deportes |

Tosha Schareina, the only man who had managed to beat Daniel Sanders this week, started the special with an overall lead of 1′42″. The Spaniard was leading the charge following his stage win yesterday, so he played it safe and managed to limit the damage to a 50-second deficit to the Australian 248 km into the 274 course. All that changed when he took the wrong turn a few minutes later, a blunder that came with a hefty price tag of 4′54″ lost to Sanders, who moved back into the hot seat. 3′12″ now separate "Chucky" and Schareina going into the finale, where the Spaniard faces an almost unsurmountable task. The man from Oz could be hours away from securing the RallyGP world championship....

epg.title: W2RC 2025: Rally Raid Portugal Stage 5
epg.desc:
| +TP | Deportes |

Daniel Sanders will forever be remembered as the first rider to claim the RallyGP title before the last event of the series. The Australian, who had been going from strength to strength in the three previous rounds, took it up to the fourth dimension in Lisbon. He crossed the finish line with 3′40″ to spare over runner-up Tosha Schareina (Monster Energy Honda HRC), who proved unable to defend his title. "Chucky", who nabbed four specials out of six, is the fourth rider to sit on the FIM throne in rally raids, following Sam Sunderland (2022), Luciano Benavides (2023) and Ross Branch (2024). His stats are out of this world, including records for the most RallyGP specials won in a single...

epg.title: Mi casa es la tuya
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Por primera vez, Boris Izaguirre abre las puertas de su casa para recibir a Bertín Osborne y hablar sin tapujos de su vida "de telenovela", como él mismo la define, entre Venezuela y España. Además, contará sus experiencias con aquellos que le insultaban por su condición sexual.

epg.title: Mi casa es la tuya
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Juanes visita la casa de Bertín acompañado de sus compañeros de "La Voz": Pablo López, Malú y Manuel Carrasco. Disfrutan de unas buenas arepas preparadas por el artista colombiano y los cuatro cantan algunos de sus éxitos más sonados.

epg.title: En el punto de mira
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

María Miñana investigará el negocio de las bodas.

epg.title: En el punto de mira
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Se abordará el negocio de los productos artesanos, en los que el etiquetado no es siempre fiel a la calidad del producto que ofrece.

epg.title: Planeta Calleja
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

El exótico y desconocido paisaje de Madagascar es el destino de Álex González. El protagonista de 'El Príncipe' y Jesús Calleja hacen frente a un reto de supervivencia atravesando el archipiélago de Nosy Hara en kayak, buscándose la vida para conseguir comida y durmiendo donde pueden.

epg.title: Planeta Calleja
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Jesús Calleja y Andrés Velencoso emprenden un nuevo reto. Su destino exacto está en la región de Phong Nga, una zona del interior del país considerada una de las mayores zonas kársticas del mundo y donde en los últimos años se han descubierto las cuevas más grandes del planeta.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Comienza la última temporada de "Los Gipsy Kings" y lo hace repleta de sopresas. Acompañamos a La Rebe, Noemí Salazar y Omar Montes en momentos que serán clave en sus vidas.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Tras un encuentro con Saray, la mujer del primo de su exmarido José, Rebeca planea un acercamiento enviándole una carta. Mientras, en Plasencia, Susi se muestra muy rebelde y sorprende a la familia haciéndose un piercing sin el consentimiento de sus padres.

epg.title: Volando Voy
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

"Volando Voy" se desplaza hasta Alto Mijares, un pueblo de Castellón, para conocer a nuevos protagonistas y nuevas historias.

epg.title: Volando Voy
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Jesús Calleja llega a la comarca de Gorbeia, en Álava. Enclavado en la forntera de Álava con Vizcaya, en los municipios de Zuya (Álava) y Ceánuri (Vizcaya) y accesible por todas sus vertientes, está rodeado de un espléndido paraje natural.

epg.title: Make Up Stars
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

A las puertas de la final, los concursantes se enfrentarán a un reto de bodypainting donde deberán representar uno de los 4 elementos de la naturaleza siguiendo los consejos de la maestra Corinne Pérez.

epg.title: Make Up Stars
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Los 3 concursantes finalistas usarán todas las técnicas aprendidas en el programa en una emocionante prueba donde deben transformarse y mostrar su súper poder, un automaquillaje supervisado por la ganadora de un óscar Christine Blundell.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Los Fernández ultiman su viaje alrededor del mundo, La Rebe se prepara para confesar que tiene novio, Los Montoya ponen en marcha la nueva tienda de Saray y Las Salazar están centradas en el desfile del Orgullo Gay.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Las vidas de los Jiménez en Plasencia darán un vuelco radical. La de Rebe por haber tenido que confesar su nueva relación; la de Dani y Marisol por el proceso de asumir la noticia.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

La aventura de los Fernández-Navarro en Tailandia se alargará con un eterno viaje en tren hacia Chiang Mai. En Palma de Mallorca, José y Fali no sabrán qué hacer para disfrutar de la vida a costa de Joaquín e involucrar a Kiki en sus andanzas.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

José y Fali deciden llevar a Joaquín y a los aventureros de la familia Fernánez a nuevo destino: Kenia. Los Jiménez viven una trumática experiencia en la ecoaldea gallega.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

La cita deportiva del año en pleno Masai-Mara, los trucos de "todo a un euro" contra la alopecia y poesías para llegar al corazón de la amada.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Los reyes del Sacromonte regresan al programa en vísperas del inminente estreno de su espectáculo flamenco. Además, Cristo busca el amor y la desaparición de Naiara por fin se esclarecerá.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Decidirse a hacerse un injerto o no decidirse a seguir con el novio. Entre estas dudas trascendentales, un gran evento: la madre de todas las bodas, la de Naiara y su novio.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

Una novia arrepentida, un viaje con un destino de ensueño, una propuesta profesional que no se puede rechazar y una second date que pone de los nervios a Cristo.

epg.title: Gipsy Kings
epg.desc:
| +16 | Estilo de vida |

El día de la despedida ha llegado. "Los Gipsy Kings" se despiden con maletas de viaje y con la satisfacción de haber cumplido casi todos los sueños que se propusieron cuando empezaron.

epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

Join charismatic chef Spencer Watts at his glorious rooftop patio for a one-hour special featuring a full holiday spread, all made on the BBQ. Spencer’s festive menu is all about creative BBQ twists with his delectable, mouth-watering recipes including Burnt Orange Cranberry Marmalade, Maple Rye Pumpkin Pie, and Asparagus with Smoked Salmon Dip. Save room for the piece de Q-sistance: Smoked Turkey Two Ways. This year, take your holiday feast outside and serve up something deliciously different.

epg.title: Flour Power Holiday Specials
epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

Christmas is right around the corner and it calls for a little fun - like a twist on traditional holiday desserts! FLOUR POWER CHRISTMAS: TWISTS ON THE CLASSICS offers a new take on some of your favourites to bring you a fresh perspective and world of flavour for the holidays! Enchanting host Jessica McGovern plays off classic desserts, serving up handy hints on how to get the most out of every bite. From sweet and fluffy Gumdrop Cakes drizzled with a light lemony glaze to a delectable Eggnog Ski Slope Cake decorated with rosemary trees and a few friends to hit the hills, Jessica's unique holiday recipes will surly make it on your list of Christmas traditions!

epg.title: The Wizard of Whatever: Holiday Edition
epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

Gusto TV’s Wizard of Whatever, Chef Kyle Crawford, is dishing up a holiday feast! There’ll be food, fun, elves… and even jolly old St. Nick himself may make an appearance! Join in as Kyle cooks up a Christmas goose complete with stuffing and gravy, plus all the sides and salads, and even a flashy flambé dessert! Merry whatever!

epg.title: Michael Bonacini's Christmas at the Farm
epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

In this heartwarming holiday special, Chef Michael Bonacini invites us to his cozy farmhouse in Ontario for a charming Christmas feast. In this scenic winter retreat, Bonacini interprets classic Welsh and Italian Christmas dishes from his childhood. Michael cooks up comforting dishes from hearty potato leek soup, to succulent roast lamb, to classic molten chocolate lava cake. As he explores homey Christmas flavours, Michael shares his traditions and gives tips for perfecting the holiday meal.

epg.title: Watts Up for the Holidays
epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

In this cheerful one-hour special, charming bachelor Spencer takes you through all the planning tips and lets you in on his secrets to create the ultimate holiday meal.

epg.title: Flour Power Holiday Specials
epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

The holidays are here! And the holidays come with a lineup of treats you won't be able to resist! From sweet and salty to traditional and unconventional, FLOUR POWER CHRISTMAS: BIG WOW DESSERTS covers it all. To get in the holiday spirit, enchanting host Jessica McGovern introduces two desserts that could impress any Scrooge. First, Jessica bakes a decadent Chocolate Yule Log stuffed with a creamy Salted Caramel Frosting and finishes with a holiday-inspired cake decorated with homemade peppermint candy canes! Interwoven with tricks of the trade, Jessica guides us through her simple yet inspiring treats that are perfect for a big Christmas celebration.

epg.title: One World Kitchen: Our Favourite Holiday Recipes
epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

In this special holiday episode of One World Kitchen, Hana (Japan), Vanessa (Italy), Natalia (Argentina), and Pailin (Thailand) get together to cook their favorite traditional holiday dishes influenced by their respective cultures. Christmas Sushi Rolls, Veal in a Creamy Tuna Sauce with Capers, Striped Bass in Garlic and Lime Marinade, and an epic Timballo. For the final recipe, our hosts combine all the flavors of One World Kitchen into a truly internationally-inspired turkey dish.

epg.title: Bonacini's Italian Christmas
epg.desc:
| +7 | Cocina y comida |

Michael takes us on a holiday culinary journey as he explores homey Christmas flavours and traditions, offering tips for perfecting dishes from the regions of Veneto, Sardinia, Calabria, Sicily, and Emilia Romagna.

epg.title: Flour Power Holiday Specials

Fun host Jessica McGovern shows us how to bake something for everyone including Crispy Brittle Bark covered in chocolate, rich Coal Cookies that are sweet with a bit of heat, adorable peanut butter-chocolate Reindeer Cupcakes, and easy-to-make Christmas Puzzle Cookies.

epg.desc:

epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.desc:

epg.desc:

| +7 | Infantil |

epg.desc:

epg.desc:

epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

La Bruja Aburrida va de bólido intentando que las niñas no tengan éxito pero, como siempre, la que no se sale con la suya es ella.

epg.title: Las Tres Mellizas
epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.title: Las Tres Mellizas
epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.title: Las Tres Mellizas
epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

epg.title: Las Tres Mellizas
epg.desc:
| +7 | Infantil |

De pronto aparece el capitán Nemo, que las acoge en su Nautilus, y les cuenta su vida y el motivo de su aislamiento.

The Angry Planet team heads to Africa to climb the steep and very active Nyiragongo Volcano in the Congo that erupted in 2002, sending 125,000 people fleeing for their lives. Host/adventurer George Kourounis explores the bubbling lake of molten lava and investigates the risk the dangerous volcano poses to both the people of city of Goma and the Mountain Gorillas who live on the nearby jungle slopes.

epg.title: Angry Planet
epg.desc:
| +TP | Estilo de vida |

Host George Kourounis has braved many terrifying phenomena – but none as frightening as the one he takes on in this episode: marriage! To make sure his new bride is on the same adventurous page with him, he proposes to get married on the lip of an exploding volcano, on the South Pacific island of Tanna, in Vanuatu. Before the native preacher, dressed in grass skirt and kustom garb, gets to perform the smoky vows, George descends into the erupting volcano to bring out red hot samples of the lava it is producing.

epg.title: SABOREANDO CHINA
epg.desc:
| +7 | Asian |

Aprenda a preparar las recetas más populares de China. Nuestro chef le revelará de forma práctica los secretos del arte culinario de esta nación asiática. Conozca los ingredientes más utilizados en la variada cocina regional, los orígenes de los platos e incluso sus beneficios para la salud. En De China a tu cocina, el espectador podrá experimentar a la vez la riqueza tradicional y la variedad gastronómica de China.

epg.title: NIHAO CHINA
epg.desc:
| +7 | Asian |

Es la clase de chino de CGTN-Español. Las series “Aprendamos juntos pinyin”, “Comunícate en chino” y “Viajando y aprendiendo chino”, abordan diferentes niveles de aprendizaje de la nueva lengua de moda en el mundo, brindando así a los televidentes la posibilidad de ampliar su vocabulario, mejorar su gramática y dominar las frases y expresiones más usuales del idioma con más hablantes en el planeta.

epg.title: DOCUMENTAL

epg.desc:
| +7 | Asian |

También le acerca a la vida y las costumbres de la gente común y le muestra la evolución del país en aspectos como educación, sociedad y protección del medio ambiente y del patrimonio histórico y natural.
